oasis.names.tc.saml._2_0.assertion_

Class SubjectConfirmationType

  • java.lang.Object
    • oasis.names.tc.saml._2_0.assertion_.SubjectConfirmationType

  • public class SubjectConfirmationType
extends Object
    Section 3.4.1: The SubjectConfirmationType is restricted to only contain a NameID and not a BaseID or EncryptedID. It must also contain the SubjectConfirmationData element Note: The NameID element is present if the token is delegated in which case it contains the identity of the delegate.

    Java class for SubjectConfirmationType complex type.

       </sequence>

 </complexType>
